    "Quantitative Analysis: Alongside expert assessment, quantitative metrics were employed to evaluate the models' performances.",
    "These metrics provided objective data on various aspects of interpretability and explainability. 7.",
    "Iterative Feedback Loop: Feedback from the initial rounds of evaluation was used to refine the experiment.",
    "This iterative process allowed for the adjustment of model settings and benchmark parameters to explore different aspects of model performance. 8.",
    "Final Analysis and Comparison: The final step involved a comprehensive analysis of all collected data, comparing the models' performances across benchmarks and evaluation criteria."
